<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>org.feichtmeier.Musicpod</id>
  
  <name>musicpod</name>
  <summary>Music, podcast and internet radio player</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-3.0</project_license>
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/ubuntu-flutter-community/musicpod</url>
  
  <description>
    <p>A Music, podcasts, and internet radio player built with Flutter for your Linux Desktop</p>
    <p>Musicpod isn't <em>just</em> a music player. You can browse podcasts or listen to internet radio stations - all in one app!</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Play local audio files (mp3, flac, mp4, ogg)</li>
        <li>Find your local audio library sorted by metadata</li>
        <li>Search for local audio files sorted by title, album, genre and artist instantly</li>
        <li>Play internet radio and TV stations and search them by tag, name or country, with icytags displayed and images loaded on demand!</li>
        <li>Play podcasts and find them by country, topic and name</li>
        <li>Download podcasts</li>
        <li>Video podcast support!</li>
        <li>Pin your favorite albums</li>
        <li>Subscribe to podcasts</li>
        <li>Gather a collection of your favorite radio/TV stations</li>
        <li>Jump easily between local audio genres and radio station genres</li>
        <li>Collect your favorite songs with the heart button</li>
    <li>And much, much more!</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
<developer id="org.feichtmeier">
